{{!-- Executive Summary --}}
<div class="page">
  {{> page-header title="Executive Summary"}}

  <h2>Scores at a Glance — Mobile</h2>
  <div class="scores-grid scores-grid-4">
    {{{scoreGaugeLarge audit.scores.seo "SEO"}}}
    {{{scoreGaugeLarge audit.scores.performance "Performance"}}}
    {{{scoreGaugeLarge audit.scores.accessibility "Accessibility"}}}
    {{{scoreGaugeLarge audit.scores.bestPractices "Best Practices"}}}
  </div>

  {{#if audit.desktopScores}}
  <h2 style="margin-top: 24px">Scores at a Glance — Desktop</h2>
  <div class="scores-grid scores-grid-4">
    {{{scoreGaugeLarge audit.desktopScores.seo "SEO"}}}
    {{{scoreGaugeLarge audit.desktopScores.performance "Performance"}}}
    {{{scoreGaugeLarge audit.desktopScores.accessibility "Accessibility"}}}
    {{{scoreGaugeLarge audit.desktopScores.bestPractices "Best Practices"}}}
  </div>
  {{/if}}

  <div class="section-divider"></div>

  <div class="summary-text">
    <p>
      We conducted a comprehensive SEO audit of <strong>{{client.domain}}</strong>,
      analyzing <strong>{{formatNumber audit.pagesCrawled}}</strong> pages for technical SEO issues,
      performance bottlenecks, and content optimization opportunities.
    </p>
    <p>
      Your site achieved an overall SEO score of <strong style="color: {{scoreColor audit.scores.seo}}">{{round audit.scores.seo}}/100</strong>
      ({{scoreLabel audit.scores.seo}}).
      We identified <strong>{{criticalCount}}</strong> critical issues requiring immediate attention,
      <strong>{{warningCount}}</strong> warnings, and
      <strong>{{infoCount}}</strong> informational items.
    </p>
    <p>
      Mobile performance scored {{round audit.scores.performance}}/100 with a Largest Contentful Paint
      of {{formatMs audit.coreWebVitals.lcp.value}}.
      {{#if audit.desktopScores}}
      Desktop performance scored {{round audit.desktopScores.performance}}/100.
      {{/if}}
      Addressing the critical issues below will have the most significant impact on your search visibility.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="priority-box">
    <h3>Top 3 Priorities</h3>
    <ol>
      {{#each topPriorities}}
      <li><strong>{{this.category}}:</strong> {{this.message}} ({{this.pagesAffected}} {{pluralize this.pagesAffected "page" "pages"}})</li>
      {{/each}}
    </ol>
  </div>

  {{> page-footer pageNum="2"}}
</div>
